TITLE: Implementing Error Handling Middleware in Hono
DESCRIPTION: Example of using Stoker's onError middleware with Hono for standardized error handling. This middleware formats errors as JSON responses and includes stack traces in non-production environments.
SOURCE: https://github.com/w3cj/stoker/blob/main/README.md#2025-04-22_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
import { Hono } from "hono";

import onError from "stoker/middlewares/on-error";

const app = new Hono();

app.onError(onError);

export default app;
```

