TITLE: Implementing 404 Not Found Middleware in Hono
DESCRIPTION: Example of using Stoker's notFound middleware with Hono to handle routes that don't exist. This provides a standardized JSON response with the appropriate 404 status code.
SOURCE: https://github.com/w3cj/stoker/blob/main/README.md#2025-04-22_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
import { Hono } from "hono";

import notFound from "stoker/middlewares/not-found";

const app = new Hono();

app.notFound(notFound);

export default app;
```

