TITLE: Creating JSON Content Schema for OpenAPI
DESCRIPTION: Example of using Stoker's jsonContent helper to create a content/schema description with application/json type for OpenAPI documentation. This simplifies defining JSON response schemas.
SOURCE: https://github.com/w3cj/stoker/blob/main/README.md#2025-04-22_snippet_6

LANGUAGE: typescript
