TITLE: Using HTTP Status Phrases with Stoker
DESCRIPTION: Example demonstrating how to use HTTP status phrase constants from Stoker. These provide semantic text representations of HTTP status codes.
SOURCE: https://github.com/w3cj/stoker/blob/main/README.md#2025-04-22_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
